---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Unit Converter"
  description="Unit Converter's privacy policy. We collect minimal data, use no tracking cookies, and never sell personal information. Read what we store and why."
  canonical="https://prounitconverter.com/privacy"
>
  <div class="container page-container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-meta">Last updated: June 2025</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Your privacy matters to us. This page explains what information Unit Converter collects,
        how it is used, and what rights you have. We have designed this tool to collect as little
        data as possible.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Server Access Logs</h3>
      <p>
        Like all web servers, our hosting provider automatically records standard access log data
        when you visit a page — including your IP address, browser type, operating system,
        referring URL, and the date and time of your request. These logs are retained for a
        limited period for security and diagnostic purposes only and are not used for advertising
        or profiling.
      </p>

      <h3>Browser Local Storage</h3>
      <p>
        We store one value in your browser's <code>localStorage</code>: your theme preference
        (light or dark mode), saved under the key <code>uc_theme</code>. This data never leaves
        your device and is not accessible to us.
      </p>

      <h3>Session Storage</h3>
      <p>
        When you use the Currency Converter, live exchange rates are cached in your browser's
        <code>sessionStorage</code> under the key <code>fx_rates</code>. This cache clears
        automatically when you close the tab and is never transmitted to our servers.
      </p>

      <h2>2. What We Do Not Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We do not collect your name, email address, or personal details unless you contact us.</li>
        <li>We do not use advertising cookies or cross-site tracking cookies.</li>
        <li>We do not track your conversion history or the values you enter into the converter.</li>
        <li>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</li>
        <li>We do not use fingerprinting or device-level tracking technologies.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>

      <h3>Exchange Rate API</h3>
      <p>
        The Currency Converter fetches live exchange rates from <strong>open.er-api.com</strong>.
        When this request is made, your browser contacts their servers directly. Please refer to
        their privacy policy for information on how they handle requests.
      </p>

      <h3>Google Fonts</h3>
      <p>
        We load the Inter typeface from Google Fonts (fonts.googleapis.com). This causes your
        browser to make a request to Google's servers on your first visit. Google may log this
        request. If you prefer, you can block external fonts in your browser; the site falls back
        to system fonts gracefully.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Unit Converter does not set any cookies. We use <code>localStorage</code> for your
        theme preference only — which is not a cookie and is never transmitted to any server.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use privacy-friendly, cookieless analytics to understand overall traffic patterns
        and which converters are most popular. If analytics are in use, no personal identifiers
        are collected or stored.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Unit Converter does not knowingly collect information from children under 13. The site
        has no user accounts, no registration process, and no way to submit personal information
        other than the optional contact form.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with
        an updated "Last updated" date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy or wish to make a data-related request,
        please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
